2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses deep learning strategies to solve the aforementioned tasks. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel approach to address challenging problems in low-level vision tasks. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with image processing and manipulation. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a transferrable pipeline that can be applied to different problem domains related to image processing.
